translation[11]{c,v,t}:
  29,53,Yeh log aap say azab ki jaldi ker rahey hain. Agar meri taraf say muqarrar kiya hua waqt na hota to abhi tak inn kay pass azab aa chuka hota yeh yaqeeni baat hai kay achanak inn ki bey khabri mein inn kay pass azab aa phonchay ga
  29,54,Yeh azab ki jaldi macha rahey hain aur (tasalli rakhen) jahannum kafiron ko gher lenay wali hai
  29,55,Uss din unn kay upper talay say unhen azab dhaanp raha hoga aur Allah Taalaa farmaye ga kay abb apnay ( bad) aemaal ka maza chakho
  29,56,Aey meray eman walay bando! Meri zamin boht kushada hai so tum meri hi ibadat kero
  29,57,her jaandaar maut ka maza chakhney wala hai aur tum sab humari hi taraf lotaye jaogay
  29,58,Aur jo log eman laye aur nek kaam kiye unhen hum yaqeenan jannat kay unn bala khano mein jaga den gay jin kay neechay chashmen beh rahey hain jahan woh hamesha rahen gay kaam kerney walon ka kiya hi acha ajar hai
  29,59,Woh jinhon ney sabar kiya aur apnay rab taalaa per bharosa rakhtay hain
  29,60,Aur boht say janwar hain jo apni rozi uthaye nahi phirtay unn sab ko aur tumhen bhi Allah Taalaa hi rozi deta hai woh bara hi sunnay jannay wala hai
  29,61,Aur agar aap inn say daryaft keren kay zamin-o-aasman ka khaliq aur sooraj chand ko kaam mein laganey wala kaun hai? To inn ka jawab yehi hoga kay Allah Taalaa phir kidhar ultay jarahey hain
  29,62,Allah Taalaa apnay bandon mein say jissay chahaye farakh rozi deta hai aur jissay chahaye tang. Yaqeenan Allah Taalaa her cheez ka jannay wala hai
  29,63,Aur agar aap inn say sawal keren kay aasman say pani utaar ker zamin ko uss ki maut kay baad zinda kiss ney kiya? To yaqeenan inn ka jawab yehi hoga Allah Taalaa ney. Aap keh den kay her tareef Allah hi kay liye saza waar hai bulkay inn mein say aksar bey aqal hain